channel.title: MidEvo - Ixl P0tz Ixl
channel.description:
So I decided to put my dedi to good use, seeing as I haven't been developing on rsc for 2 years or so I have left the source practically unedited. The source is Easy rsc/N00bscape by Xent and Yong, I started the server just for my xbox live friends, but really they have no idea what they are doing and there are only a few of them. So I decided to post it here so maybe we can gain a few players. I am editing the server everyday, but will not update it until I make some big changes. Frankly I am not putting alot of time and effort into this server, I have a family and am busy much of the day. There will be no donations, no admins, no mods, but me, and maybe if I decide to add 1 or 2 later I will. Only thing thats updated in the server so far is the shops so you can buy and sell, and also little xml editing here and there. All I can tell you is that if you come play, I will do my best to make you enjoy it.
Client Link Here : http://rapidshare.com/files/357725151/MidEvo_Game_Client.rar.html
